214_1" type="commentary"/><rs ref="#pmb31085" type="work"><hi rend="latintype">Francesca</hi></rs><note xml:id="K_L01214_1h" type="commentary">Am <date>2. 4. 1902</date> besuchte <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler</rs> die Vorführung von <rs ref="#pmb31085" type="work">Francesca da Rimini</rs> mit <rs type="person" ref="#pmb11201">Eleonora Duse</rs> im <rs type="place" ref="#pmb77">Raimund-Theater</rs>.</note>«?</p><closer>Von Herzen Ihr<lb/><signed>Hugo.</signed></closer></div></body><back><listPerson><person xml:id="pmb11740">
